	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Not if you resistance is high enough to not draw too much current, but is low enough to make a significan difference than when the pin is open. 470 ohm should do the work I guess. If you want, you could do exact calculation with 5 vols divided by the maximum current you want, etc, etc...

		

